title: Archaic Kinds Of Fun
body:
What’s the most impossible job you can think of? For Jo Holbrook, The Tank, Killer Extradonaire…it’s being a bodyguard. Leave it to Fury to kick it up a notch. Now she’s playing chauffeur for Tony Stark and trying to figure out where her life went wrong. At least there’s pancakes.

For The Record

November 1, 2014DARCY“Yo, Skye! You in here?!” Darcy called out as she walked into Tony’s lab. She heard music, and she knew Tony wasn’t playing it because he was out on a date with Pepper…

summary: Ant-Man & The Wasp (2018) As Scott Lang balances being both a Super Hero and a father, Hope van Dyne and Dr. Hank Pym present an...
caption:
Ant-Man & The Wasp (2018)

As Scott Lang balances being both a Super Hero and a father, Hope van Dyne and Dr. Hank Pym present an urgent new mission that finds the Ant-Man fighting alongside The Wasp to uncover secrets from their past.

One of the weakest Marvel movies to date. It’s like they just made the sequel (to the very entertaining first film) just for the sake of making a sequel. There is no thought given to the plot. It’s mediocre at best. There are some funny parts in it, but the film is incredibly weak and pointless.

There are two post credit scenes. The second scene is pointless and you don’t need to waste your time on it. In fact, don’t waste your time on this film and wait for it to come on TV and then fast forward it so you are “up to date” with the “story”.

summary: omg congrats on 1k!!! I’d like a Marvel ship if you don’t mind :) I’m a straight female, 5’5”, brown hair and eyes and I wear...
question: omg congrats on 1k!!! I’d like a Marvel ship if you don’t mind :) I’m a straight female, 5’5”, brown hair and eyes and I wear glasses. I love soft things and bullet journals and dogs and vine references and Disney movies! I’m a very sun, moon and stars kind of girl, if that makes any sense haha. I’ve always been into the soft but protective type of guy. thank you in advance!!!
answer:
thank you omg! x 

I ship you with… 

Thor! 

- thor would totally love to watch disney movies with you, finding himself maybe too emotionally invested in the characters. after discovering his love for the lion king you’d start calling him simba, which he’d love more than he’d care to admit. quoting disney movies back and forth would be your cute couple thing. 

- because of your love for dogs, i can for sure see thor surprising you with one for your birthday, the grin on your face lighting up his heart and his cheeks. (named after a disney dog, of course. pluto or doug maybe) 

- you and thor would love to stargaze together on the balcony, legs dangling 60 floors above the concrete below and talking for hours. he’d tell you stories of all of realms and planets he’d visited, and you’d share your childhood memories and your deepest aspirations. often times you’d lose track of time and fall asleep outside, his arms wrapped around you tightly with the stars watching over. 

thank you again!! x 

Want one?

Marvel ship requests are open!

Firstly I’ll start off by saying that I’m really sorry that I’ve been off Tumblr for so long and even though only one or two people will read this I felt obligated to give a brief explanation. Things have been crazy with work and my training as well as a stressed family.

Anywho I hope somebody will request because I’d love to do some writing even though I’m really rusty. Sorry again if your request wasn’t done but if you’d still like me to write one I’d be really happy to.

Once again I’m really sorry and I hope to make it up to all of you.
